WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.760
For many Muslims, faith includes a quiet daily rhythm,

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:06.160
repeating short prayers that remember God,

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:08.200
often counted on prayer beads.

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:10.680
Misbaha helps them stay consistent,

00:00:10.680 --> 00:00:13.600
counting each phrase, following plans,

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:14.920
and tracking progress.

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:18.320
Today shows daily counts, lifetime totals,

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:20.760
active goals, and early activity.

00:00:20.760 --> 00:00:23.440
The counter organizes prayers by category:

00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:25.440
scripture, morning and evening,

00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:27.040
worship, and hardship.

00:00:27.040 --> 00:00:29.700
Search by English spelling or Arabic script,

00:00:29.700 --> 00:00:31.960
on the counter screen or inside goals.

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:34.680
The same search works when planning goals.

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:36.800
Pick prayers and drop them into your plan.

00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:41.080
Open any prayer for text, translation, and references.

00:00:41.080 --> 00:00:43.680
Double tap to count, hold to complete.

00:00:43.680 --> 00:00:46.040
Goals turn remembrance into plans:

00:00:46.040 --> 00:00:50.880
suggested paths, surprise challenges, or custom rotations.

00:00:50.880 --> 00:00:53.000
Each goal focuses one prayer per day

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.200
with progress tracking and a quick counter.

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:57.920
Plan a new goal by choosing prayers and duration.

00:00:57.920 --> 00:01:00.640
Visualize three ways: a growing garden,

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:03.800
a walk across the earth, or a rise into the stars.

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:07.160
Earn badges as you count, finish prayer cycles,

00:01:07.160 --> 00:01:11.060
keep streaks, complete goals, and try new prayers.

00:01:11.060 --> 00:01:13.760
Each milestone unlocks the next set of 10.

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:17.880
Tune counts per tap, themes, language, sound,

00:01:17.880 --> 00:01:18.800
and haptics.

00:01:18.800 --> 00:01:21.240
Misbaha — counting, goals,

00:01:21.240 --> 00:01:23.900
and visual journeys from Zikr Apps.
